      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LONG GULLY LARRY (1) was checked in the run and safely held when fourth (20.55) in a Other over 342m at this track. Has good early burn and suited drawn the inside. Has the ability and looks a key chance. SHE'S GOT DESIGN (4) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (19.86) behind Switching Lanes at this track. Has good early speed so she should be prominent despite the squeeze draw. Leading chance. RINGO ROSE (2) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Finished third (20.56) at this track last time making it three minors on end. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Expected to be in this for a long way. ADHANA ROY (8) is worth including.",
